1
00:00:22,620 --> 00:00:26,000
♪The blood within me ignites
with a fierce desire♪

2
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:29,300
♪Exposing the lies
that fate has written♪

3
00:00:29,300 --> 00:00:30,760
♪No more hiding♪

4
00:00:30,760 --> 00:00:33,860
♪My martial soul has awakened
in its full strength♪

5
00:00:35,570 --> 00:00:38,760
♪Even countless of trials can't stop me♪

6
00:00:38,760 --> 00:00:42,050
♪The searing heat
that surges within my chest♪

7
00:00:42,050 --> 00:00:43,440
♪I want the world♪

8
00:00:43,440 --> 00:00:47,220
♪To remember me♪

9
00:00:48,090 --> 00:00:51,930
♪Yes or no, right or wrong♪

10
00:00:51,930 --> 00:00:53,640
♪To defeat or to be defeated♪

11
00:00:53,640 --> 00:00:56,940
♪Giving my all with no regrets♪

12
00:00:57,200 --> 00:00:58,880
♪Breaking through the encirclement♪

13
00:00:58,880 --> 00:01:02,030
♪It doesn't matter who my opponent is♪

14
00:01:02,030 --> 00:01:05,230
♪To shine as the new star
of Douluo Continent♪

15
00:01:05,230 --> 00:01:06,630
♪The fleeting dream of life is
easily shattered♪

16
00:01:06,630 --> 00:01:10,020
♪So why not face it boldly,
just this once♪

17
00:01:10,020 --> 00:01:11,660
♪Fierce storms and raging thunder♪

18
00:01:11,660 --> 00:01:14,880
♪Burn me, yet refine my determination♪

19
00:01:14,880 --> 00:01:18,500
♪No matter how battered,
I smile and refuse to retreat♪

20
00:01:18,500 --> 00:01:22,170
♪A so-called hero, covered in dust♪

21
00:01:22,840 --> 00:01:24,990
♪Scarred and worn♪

22
00:01:24,990 --> 00:01:26,980
♪Can still sever the cycle of fate♪

23
00:01:26,980 --> 00:01:28,320
=The Land of Warriors=

24
00:01:28,321 --> 00:01:29,980
(Adapted from
Tangjia Sanshao's novel "Soul Land")

25
00:01:31,220 --> 00:01:34,940
=Episode 15=

26
00:02:29,860 --> 00:02:31,020
It's a 10,000-year soul ring.

27
00:02:31,140 --> 00:02:33,420
Wu, your transformation is successful.

28
00:02:33,770 --> 00:02:35,300
But it was too risky this time.

29
00:02:36,656 --> 00:02:38,224
Sorry for making both of you worried.

30
00:02:43,300 --> 00:02:44,700
We were not the only ones.

31
00:02:45,170 --> 00:02:47,050
Tang San was pretty worried too.

32
00:02:47,540 --> 00:02:49,696
The Blue Silver Plants
around us were so frantic

33
00:02:49,712 --> 00:02:51,760
that they were about
to spring out of the ground.

34
00:02:52,300 --> 00:02:55,330
But Tang San seems to be quite capable.

35
00:02:55,824 --> 00:02:58,384
He could actually help you
through the Blue Silver Bracelet.

36
00:02:58,860 --> 00:02:59,980
I

37
00:03:00,100 --> 00:03:01,860
can admire him a little for a while.

38
00:03:05,260 --> 00:03:06,260
It's all thanks to him.

39
00:03:07,050 --> 00:03:08,260
Otherwise,

40
00:03:08,480 --> 00:03:10,100
I would remain trapped in the nightmare,

41
00:03:10,140 --> 00:03:11,020
unable to break free.

42
00:03:13,580 --> 00:03:15,890
You clearly underwent the trial yourself

43
00:03:16,330 --> 00:03:17,580
for the soul ring conversion.

44
00:03:18,050 --> 00:03:20,450
You can't succeed by relying on others.

45
00:03:23,820 --> 00:03:25,890
Daming appears to be stubborn

46
00:03:25,936 --> 00:03:27,170
but he's soft on the inside.

47
00:03:38,450 --> 00:03:39,610
What a miserable scream.

48
00:03:40,100 --> 00:03:40,930
What happened?

49
00:03:48,896 --> 00:03:50,610
Those scums from the Martial Soul Hall

50
00:03:50,736 --> 00:03:52,192
actually triggered a beast horde.

51
00:03:52,352 --> 00:03:53,580
I'm sure Xingdou Forest is now

52
00:03:53,580 --> 00:03:54,860
in complete chaos.

53
00:03:55,930 --> 00:03:56,610
But

54
00:03:56,770 --> 00:03:59,210
the beast horde made
the Martial Soul Hall hesitate.

55
00:03:59,490 --> 00:04:01,260
They never appeared again after that.

56
00:04:01,490 --> 00:04:03,380
No, they were here for me.

57
00:04:03,424 --> 00:04:04,930
They will find a chance to return.

58
00:04:06,100 --> 00:04:07,300
Xingdou Forest cannot afford

59
00:04:07,300 --> 00:04:08,688
to experience another beast horde.

60
00:04:08,930 --> 00:04:09,890
I need to find a way.

61
00:04:15,770 --> 00:04:16,450
Your Highnesses.

62
00:04:16,704 --> 00:04:18,112
That's all for today's training.

63
00:04:18,210 --> 00:04:19,136
Get some proper rest.

64
00:04:26,140 --> 00:04:26,580
Zhuqing.

65
00:04:49,970 --> 00:04:51,180
If San and the rest are here,

66
00:04:51,264 --> 00:04:52,832
San would be in charge of controlling,

67
00:04:53,060 --> 00:04:54,210
Fatty and I on attack,

68
00:04:54,530 --> 00:04:55,650
Ao and Rongrong as support.

69
00:04:55,888 --> 00:04:57,328
Two Soul Saints would mean nothing.

70
00:04:57,620 --> 00:04:58,330
I'd be fine even

71
00:04:58,784 --> 00:05:00,144
if two more showed up.

72
00:05:01,330 --> 00:05:03,620
Your Highness, you're sure impressive.

73
00:05:03,970 --> 00:05:06,260
You're even looking for help
with your training?

74
00:05:11,664 --> 00:05:13,330
I'm serious about bringing them here.

75
00:05:13,740 --> 00:05:15,180
If the Seven Devils gather,

76
00:05:15,500 --> 00:05:16,580
it will be of great help

77
00:05:16,580 --> 00:05:17,740
to Xingluo's future.

78
00:05:18,260 --> 00:05:19,232
I have it all planned.

79
00:05:19,620 --> 00:05:20,650
When we meet again,

80
00:05:20,720 --> 00:05:22,384
I'll use my position as the Crown Prince

81
00:05:22,880 --> 00:05:23,970
to invite them officially.

82
00:05:24,048 --> 00:05:25,210
I will give them the best...

83
00:05:25,210 --> 00:05:26,210
Let's not think

84
00:05:26,784 --> 00:05:28,330
about something too far in the future.

85
00:05:29,180 --> 00:05:30,970
We can think about the future

86
00:05:31,088 --> 00:05:33,088
after we honor our promise
to His Majesty.

87
00:05:34,380 --> 00:05:34,890
Zhuqing,

88
00:05:35,232 --> 00:05:36,272
is there anything wrong?

89
00:05:37,740 --> 00:05:38,330
Report!

90
00:05:41,536 --> 00:05:42,330
Your Highness.

91
00:05:43,456 --> 00:05:44,770
This is our training ground.

92
00:05:45,410 --> 00:05:46,620
Who says you can barge in?

93
00:05:46,820 --> 00:05:47,380
Your Highness,

94
00:05:47,424 --> 00:05:48,720
someone intrude into the palace.

95
00:05:48,736 --> 00:05:49,820
I really have no other way.

96
00:05:50,090 --> 00:05:51,020
You can report this

97
00:05:51,090 --> 00:05:52,672
to the Commander of the Imperial Guard.

98
00:05:52,672 --> 00:05:53,580
Why did you come here?

99
00:05:53,700 --> 00:05:54,650
But that person insisted

100
00:05:54,740 --> 00:05:56,608
that he is a close friend
of Your Highnesses.

101
00:05:56,608 --> 00:05:57,890
So we dare not act recklessly.

102
00:05:58,000 --> 00:05:58,768
So we could only...

103
00:06:01,850 --> 00:06:02,940
Let me go!

104
00:06:04,740 --> 00:06:05,820
Release me!

105
00:06:14,450 --> 00:06:15,180
Boss Dai!

106
00:06:15,290 --> 00:06:16,060
Zhuqing!

107
00:06:16,260 --> 00:06:17,180
Help me!

108
00:06:17,488 --> 00:06:18,380
- Fatty?
- Fatty?

109
00:06:24,740 --> 00:06:25,700
Satisfying.

110
00:06:26,210 --> 00:06:27,330
Absolutely satisfying.

111
00:06:27,530 --> 00:06:28,740
This is the best meal I've had

112
00:06:28,890 --> 00:06:30,380
since leaving the academy.

113
00:06:32,144 --> 00:06:34,208
It looks like Mr. Flander can't afford
to feed you

114
00:06:34,380 --> 00:06:35,380
and throw you out.

115
00:06:36,090 --> 00:06:37,450
The dean may be stingy.

116
00:06:37,568 --> 00:06:39,648
But not to the point
where he won't let you eat.

117
00:06:39,648 --> 00:06:41,968
I bet it's mostly
because Fatty was sloppy in his training

118
00:06:41,984 --> 00:06:43,360
and a bad influence on the juniors.

119
00:06:43,424 --> 00:06:44,090
So Ms. Erlong

120
00:06:44,210 --> 00:06:45,620
just tossed him out, right?

121
00:06:46,060 --> 00:06:48,210
Am I, Ma Hongjun,
the mighty Evil Phoenix,

122
00:06:48,560 --> 00:06:50,060
not allowed to travel the continent,

123
00:06:50,090 --> 00:06:51,140
do some good deeds,

124
00:06:51,140 --> 00:06:52,290
and care for the world?

125
00:06:52,330 --> 00:06:53,216
Of course, you can.

126
00:06:53,260 --> 00:06:55,060
But how come a chivalrous hero

127
00:06:55,290 --> 00:06:57,090
like you arrived here all tied up?

128
00:06:57,090 --> 00:06:58,020
Covered in dirt.

129
00:06:58,090 --> 00:06:59,740
Looking completely helpless.

130
00:06:59,820 --> 00:07:01,330
Stop completing each other's sentences.

131
00:07:01,940 --> 00:07:03,260
If I weren't afraid of ruining

132
00:07:03,290 --> 00:07:04,820
the Xingluo royal family's reputation,

133
00:07:05,020 --> 00:07:06,290
I would have beaten those guards

134
00:07:06,290 --> 00:07:07,330
into a pulp.

135
00:07:08,890 --> 00:07:10,940
We have laws in Xingluo.

136
00:07:10,992 --> 00:07:12,700
If you were imprisoned
because of a fight,

137
00:07:12,890 --> 00:07:14,770
Mubai and I can't help you.

138
00:07:16,140 --> 00:07:17,140
I see.

139
00:07:17,424 --> 00:07:19,620
Returning to the royal family
sure has changed you.

140
00:07:20,090 --> 00:07:21,330
I am left to fend for myself.

141
00:07:22,290 --> 00:07:22,740
Fine.

142
00:07:23,410 --> 00:07:23,890
I'll leave.

143
00:07:24,290 --> 00:07:25,380
I can just leave now.

144
00:07:27,050 --> 00:07:28,860
After taking advantage
of Xingluo's free meal,

145
00:07:28,864 --> 00:07:30,240
you can't just leave as you wish.

146
00:07:30,272 --> 00:07:31,090
You have to stay here

147
00:07:31,180 --> 00:07:32,500
and be my attendant for a month

148
00:07:32,650 --> 00:07:33,530
to cover this meal.

149
00:07:36,700 --> 00:07:37,740
To be honest,

150
00:07:38,060 --> 00:07:39,940
I do have some important news

151
00:07:40,000 --> 00:07:41,820
that could be at least worth
a hundred meals.

152
00:07:43,740 --> 00:07:45,020
Have San and Wu returned?

153
00:07:46,290 --> 00:07:47,140
Well, no.

154
00:07:47,290 --> 00:07:48,140
When I left,

155
00:07:48,208 --> 00:07:49,696
there was still no news about them.

156
00:07:49,744 --> 00:07:51,250
Then what kind of important information

157
00:07:51,280 --> 00:07:51,840
do you have?

158
00:07:52,210 --> 00:07:54,530
I risked my life to obtain it.

159
00:07:54,940 --> 00:07:55,530
Can you guess

160
00:07:56,090 --> 00:07:57,330
who has come to Xingluo City?

161
00:07:59,740 --> 00:08:00,410
Who?

162
00:08:02,740 --> 00:08:04,180
Grand Chrysanthemum Master.

163
00:08:05,740 --> 00:08:08,180
Bi Bi Dong's subordinate,
Grand Chrysanthemum Master?

164
00:08:08,580 --> 00:08:09,330
Yes.

165
00:08:09,450 --> 00:08:10,450
How did you find out?

166
00:08:10,580 --> 00:08:11,330
Where is he now?

167
00:08:29,890 --> 00:08:31,410
Well, this is what happened.

168
00:08:31,770 --> 00:08:33,100
During my travels,

169
00:08:33,260 --> 00:08:34,650
I suddenly realized that people from

170
00:08:34,650 --> 00:08:36,250
from Martial Soul Hall
in various cities

171
00:08:36,256 --> 00:08:38,096
were recruiting high-level soul masters.

172
00:08:38,144 --> 00:08:39,180
I felt something was off

173
00:08:39,184 --> 00:08:41,020
so I pretended to respond
to the recruitment

174
00:08:41,020 --> 00:08:42,140
and followed all the way

175
00:08:42,740 --> 00:08:44,140
to Xingluo City.

176
00:08:47,072 --> 00:08:48,560
What are you looking around for?

177
00:08:48,570 --> 00:08:49,220
Your full name?

178
00:08:50,170 --> 00:08:50,740
Ma...

179
00:08:52,020 --> 00:08:52,770
Yingjun.

180
00:08:53,290 --> 00:08:54,380
Ma Yingjun.

181
00:08:55,930 --> 00:08:56,500
Ma'am,

182
00:08:56,800 --> 00:08:58,050
didn't the recruitment state

183
00:08:58,064 --> 00:09:00,560
we're here to be a teacher
at Xingluo City's Martial Soul Hall?

184
00:09:00,640 --> 00:09:02,480
Why are there so many soul masters here?

185
00:09:02,740 --> 00:09:04,380
Is there another round of elimination?

186
00:09:04,864 --> 00:09:07,040
Don't pry into matters
that don't concern you.

187
00:09:07,260 --> 00:09:08,500
Write down your name,

188
00:09:08,528 --> 00:09:09,140
martial soul,

189
00:09:09,168 --> 00:09:10,480
and the level of your soul power.

190
00:09:13,780 --> 00:09:15,980
(Ma Yingjun)

191
00:09:20,224 --> 00:09:22,512
(Ma Yingjun with Earth Dragon. 69 Soul Emperor)
Miss,

192
00:09:22,570 --> 00:09:24,340
I have three generations

193
00:09:24,340 --> 00:09:25,380
who are depending on me.

194
00:09:25,770 --> 00:09:27,020
I came all the way here.

195
00:09:27,344 --> 00:09:28,620
I won't be eliminated, right?

196
00:09:28,690 --> 00:09:29,770
Since you're here,

197
00:09:29,952 --> 00:09:31,824
there's naturally something
for you to do.

198
00:09:32,140 --> 00:09:33,050
Enough talking.

199
00:09:33,690 --> 00:09:34,530
Or else

200
00:09:34,624 --> 00:09:36,208
you wouldn't know when you're dead.

201
00:09:41,650 --> 00:09:42,570
Turn this way.

202
00:09:45,890 --> 00:09:46,930
From now on,

203
00:09:47,296 --> 00:09:49,530
you're a part of the Martial Soul Hall
in Xingluo City.

204
00:09:49,792 --> 00:09:52,384
Next, you all need to prepare
for the intensive training.

205
00:09:53,100 --> 00:09:54,620
I don't care where you're from

206
00:09:54,980 --> 00:09:55,740
or why you're here.

207
00:09:56,260 --> 00:09:57,890
All you need to remember is

208
00:09:58,290 --> 00:09:59,930
to serve Her Holiness to the death.

209
00:10:04,592 --> 00:10:05,312
This way, please.

210
00:10:06,816 --> 00:10:08,220
(Grand Chrysanthemum Master?)

211
00:10:08,410 --> 00:10:09,500
(Why is he here?)

212
00:10:12,064 --> 00:10:14,000
I ate something bad
that upset my stomach.

213
00:10:14,016 --> 00:10:15,184
I need to go to the toilet.

214
00:10:15,620 --> 00:10:16,290
Thanks.

215
00:10:35,530 --> 00:10:36,740
Why the sudden turn of events?

216
00:10:37,690 --> 00:10:38,740
It's not sudden.

217
00:10:38,944 --> 00:10:40,384
Her Holiness has waited many years

218
00:10:40,416 --> 00:10:41,824
for this day to come.

219
00:10:41,930 --> 00:10:43,890
Distribute the armors I brought.

220
00:10:44,500 --> 00:10:46,500
Act according
to Her Holiness' instructions.

221
00:10:46,770 --> 00:10:47,170
Yes.

222
00:10:47,410 --> 00:10:48,020
Then we...

223
00:10:48,890 --> 00:10:49,810
Sir.

224
00:10:50,050 --> 00:10:52,460
I... I'm here to serve tea.

225
00:11:04,620 --> 00:11:05,980
You're very skilled.

226
00:11:06,770 --> 00:11:08,410
I have learned some manners

227
00:11:08,860 --> 00:11:10,770
from the pig... Pig-headed...

228
00:11:10,930 --> 00:11:12,170
I mean the esteemed masters.

229
00:11:12,860 --> 00:11:13,340
Yes.

230
00:11:13,570 --> 00:11:15,530
He's considered
an appropriately trained servant.

231
00:11:18,340 --> 00:11:19,380
Raise your head.

232
00:11:28,930 --> 00:11:29,530
You...

233
00:11:31,020 --> 00:11:31,890
Forgive me, sir.

234
00:11:32,050 --> 00:11:34,170
I was bullied as a child

235
00:11:34,290 --> 00:11:35,220
and got hurt in my face.

236
00:11:35,360 --> 00:11:37,930
Thankfully the Martial Soul Hall
didn't mind my humble background

237
00:11:38,020 --> 00:11:38,770
and took me in.

238
00:11:38,860 --> 00:11:39,530
Get out.

239
00:11:39,690 --> 00:11:40,890
Yes, of course.

240
00:12:22,170 --> 00:12:24,410
Grand Chrysanthemum Master
sent so much armors.

241
00:12:24,530 --> 00:12:27,020
They must be up to no good.

242
00:12:32,890 --> 00:12:34,570
You burned all those armors?

243
00:12:35,140 --> 00:12:35,810
What do you say?

244
00:12:36,050 --> 00:12:37,890
Is this information worth 100 meals?

245
00:12:38,020 --> 00:12:38,500
Yes.

246
00:12:38,752 --> 00:12:39,840
It's more than worth it.

247
00:12:39,980 --> 00:12:40,530
Fatty,

248
00:12:40,720 --> 00:12:42,140
this information is very important.

249
00:12:42,530 --> 00:12:43,930
I didn't expect after so long,

250
00:12:43,984 --> 00:12:45,264
you've made such great progress.

251
00:12:45,290 --> 00:12:47,328
You even know
how to analyze problems yourself now.

252
00:12:47,376 --> 00:12:48,260
Well, of course.

253
00:12:48,528 --> 00:12:50,592
Do you think
I've been traveling around aimlessly

254
00:12:50,608 --> 00:12:51,570
these past few months?

255
00:12:51,840 --> 00:12:54,320
There were soul masters disappearing
for no reason before.

256
00:12:54,352 --> 00:12:56,368
Now, the Martial Soul Hall
is recruiting soldiers.

257
00:12:56,416 --> 00:12:57,410
Could these two things

258
00:12:57,650 --> 00:12:58,740
be related?

259
00:12:59,100 --> 00:13:00,410
It's still uncertain for now.

260
00:13:00,890 --> 00:13:02,380
But the Martial Soul Hall

261
00:13:02,400 --> 00:13:03,936
is secretly training soul masters here.

262
00:13:03,980 --> 00:13:05,088
So there's something wrong.

263
00:13:05,140 --> 00:13:06,170
No, that's not right.

264
00:13:06,930 --> 00:13:09,260
They're not training
ordinary soul masters,

265
00:13:09,740 --> 00:13:11,770
but an army of soul masters.

266
00:13:13,740 --> 00:13:14,460
Fatty,

267
00:13:15,290 --> 00:13:16,380
you have to come with me.

268
00:13:16,530 --> 00:13:17,050
Why?

269
00:13:17,260 --> 00:13:18,740
This matter is still up in the air.

270
00:13:18,800 --> 00:13:20,240
So we need to investigate further.

271
00:13:20,288 --> 00:13:21,232
After it gets dark,

272
00:13:21,260 --> 00:13:22,530
take us to the Martial Soul Hall.

273
00:13:22,784 --> 00:13:23,770
Once everything is clear,

274
00:13:23,890 --> 00:13:25,100
we'll report it to Father.

275
00:13:25,290 --> 00:13:26,340
I knew it.

276
00:13:26,460 --> 00:13:28,860
There's no free lunch
at the Xingluo royal family.

277
00:13:29,890 --> 00:13:30,890
Here, enjoy your food.

278
00:13:31,340 --> 00:13:32,340
Have some more.

279
00:13:32,570 --> 00:13:33,020
Enjoy it.

280
00:13:33,770 --> 00:13:34,860
I want chicken.

281
00:13:34,860 --> 00:13:35,340
Here you go.

282
00:13:35,340 --> 00:13:35,810
This too.

283
00:13:37,770 --> 00:13:38,740
You can all leave now.

284
00:13:48,240 --> 00:13:49,460
Why did you suddenly summon

285
00:13:49,460 --> 00:13:52,280
the heads of the Martial Soul Hall
from all cities to Martial Soul City?

286
00:13:52,340 --> 00:13:54,530
You sure are well-informed.

287
00:13:54,770 --> 00:13:55,770
Answer me.

288
00:13:56,340 --> 00:13:58,020
Don't forget your place.

289
00:13:58,770 --> 00:14:00,260
It is not your place to meddle

290
00:14:00,890 --> 00:14:02,340
in what I want to do.

291
00:14:02,650 --> 00:14:04,272
You're gathering soul masters all over

292
00:14:04,432 --> 00:14:06,416
and urgently summoning
the leaders of each hall.

293
00:14:06,410 --> 00:14:07,920
This will definitely attract attention.

294
00:14:08,016 --> 00:14:10,288
You cannot underestimate
Tiandou and Xingluo's strength.

295
00:14:10,290 --> 00:14:11,650
I need to know your plan.

296
00:14:12,260 --> 00:14:13,340
What you need to do is stay

297
00:14:13,340 --> 00:14:15,020
within the Tiandou royal family,

298
00:14:15,170 --> 00:14:16,890
and cooperate when I require it.

299
00:14:17,170 --> 00:14:18,770
The rest is not for you to question.

300
00:14:19,690 --> 00:14:22,170
The Emperor of Tiandou
won't last much longer.

301
00:14:22,240 --> 00:14:23,536
Whatever it is you plan to do,

302
00:14:23,600 --> 00:14:24,410
you can wait.

303
00:14:31,530 --> 00:14:32,460
Not bad.

304
00:14:34,530 --> 00:14:36,100
Your soul power has increased.

305
00:14:37,020 --> 00:14:37,980
But that doesn't mean

306
00:14:38,050 --> 00:14:39,770
you can challenge me.

307
00:14:41,410 --> 00:14:42,530
Don't forget why

308
00:14:42,570 --> 00:14:44,690
I sent you to infiltrate
the Tiandou royal family.

309
00:14:45,810 --> 00:14:47,170
Without my summon,

310
00:14:47,328 --> 00:14:48,260
do not show up here.

311
00:15:07,740 --> 00:15:09,530
(Could this small village used to be)

312
00:15:10,170 --> 00:15:13,260
(the greatest sect in the world?)

313
00:15:23,740 --> 00:15:25,380
Old fella, why are you here

314
00:15:25,500 --> 00:15:26,740
and why are you wearing a mask?

315
00:15:28,340 --> 00:15:28,930
Old fella?

316
00:15:31,904 --> 00:15:32,810
Are you talking to me?

317
00:15:35,456 --> 00:15:36,170
All right, then.

318
00:15:36,192 --> 00:15:37,616
You can call me whatever you want.

319
00:15:37,890 --> 00:15:38,340
Kid,

320
00:15:38,810 --> 00:15:39,570
can you tell me

321
00:15:39,696 --> 00:15:40,890
the way to the Haotian Sect?

322
00:15:44,100 --> 00:15:45,020
I've never heard of it.

323
00:15:46,100 --> 00:15:46,890
This can't be.

324
00:15:47,500 --> 00:15:48,890
This map is accurate.

325
00:15:51,690 --> 00:15:52,890
Where did you get this map?

326
00:15:53,530 --> 00:15:54,570
Do you recognize this map?

327
00:15:58,340 --> 00:16:00,410
Run for it! Quick, run!

328
00:16:00,500 --> 00:16:01,220
Hurry up, run!

329
00:16:02,140 --> 00:16:02,860
Kid,

330
00:16:03,980 --> 00:16:05,020
return the map to me.

331
00:16:05,140 --> 00:16:06,860
I'll return it to you if you come here.

332
00:16:07,340 --> 00:16:09,020
If you don't return it to me,

333
00:16:09,140 --> 00:16:11,500
this old fella is going to spank you.

334
00:16:12,260 --> 00:16:14,196
- Come on.
- We're waiting.

335
00:16:20,980 --> 00:16:22,570
- Come up here.
- Come and hit me.

336
00:16:22,690 --> 00:16:23,930
Come and spank me.

337
00:16:23,952 --> 00:16:25,650
- Come up here.
- Come and spank me.

338
00:16:25,650 --> 00:16:26,810
Come on!

339
00:16:28,340 --> 00:16:31,020
I see. You dare to make fun of me.

340
00:16:31,104 --> 00:16:31,890
Come on, let's go.

341
00:16:31,890 --> 00:16:32,570
Get someone here.

342
00:16:49,100 --> 00:16:50,220
With them keeping watch

343
00:16:50,220 --> 00:16:51,170
across Xingdou Forest,

344
00:16:51,200 --> 00:16:52,590
you will receive a warning from them

345
00:16:52,592 --> 00:16:53,990
when a large number of soul masters

346
00:16:54,128 --> 00:16:55,664
from the Martial Soul Hall come again.

347
00:16:55,810 --> 00:16:57,570
When that happens,
evacuate the soul beasts

348
00:16:57,728 --> 00:16:59,472
to avoid triggering
a larger beast horde.

349
00:17:00,100 --> 00:17:01,530
After arranging this plan,

350
00:17:02,220 --> 00:17:04,020
are you going to leave again?

351
00:17:04,530 --> 00:17:05,090
I...

352
00:17:05,460 --> 00:17:06,530
Wu...

353
00:17:07,090 --> 00:17:08,810
She should leave anyway.

354
00:17:09,090 --> 00:17:11,370
She's always talking about Tang San,

355
00:17:11,610 --> 00:17:13,136
thinking about him day and night.

356
00:17:13,216 --> 00:17:15,370
Leaving here means
she can reunite with him.

357
00:17:15,648 --> 00:17:16,810
Besides, Wu hasn't reached

358
00:17:16,810 --> 00:17:18,260
the six-ring Mature Phase yet.

359
00:17:18,700 --> 00:17:20,810
Leaving this chaotic Xingdou Forest

360
00:17:20,810 --> 00:17:21,984
and staying out of trouble

361
00:17:22,530 --> 00:17:23,980
might not be a bad idea.

362
00:17:24,810 --> 00:17:25,570
Erming,

363
00:17:26,180 --> 00:17:27,330
you've just said

364
00:17:28,020 --> 00:17:29,740
that Xingdou Forest is in chaos now.

365
00:17:29,980 --> 00:17:31,180
How can I leave?

366
00:17:31,850 --> 00:17:32,460
Really?

367
00:17:32,660 --> 00:17:33,792
You're not leaving anymore?

368
00:17:33,840 --> 00:17:35,700
The Martial Soul Hall is here
because of me.

369
00:17:35,760 --> 00:17:37,536
I'm also responsible
for the beast horde.

370
00:17:37,776 --> 00:17:38,660
I would never leave

371
00:17:38,740 --> 00:17:40,500
when Xingdou Forest

372
00:17:40,810 --> 00:17:41,940
is in such chaos.

373
00:17:42,330 --> 00:17:43,700
Then what do you plan to do?

374
00:17:44,960 --> 00:17:47,370
I need to visit the peripheral area
and mixed zone first

375
00:17:47,504 --> 00:17:49,104
before figuring out what to do next.

376
00:17:49,130 --> 00:17:49,850
Wu,

377
00:17:50,020 --> 00:17:51,050
I'll go with you.

378
00:17:51,330 --> 00:17:52,220
You cannot.

379
00:17:52,740 --> 00:17:54,980
Don't forget
you're a Hectomillennium Fierce Beast.

380
00:17:55,220 --> 00:17:56,050
One roar from you,

381
00:17:56,050 --> 00:17:57,872
the soul beasts
will be trembling with fear.

382
00:17:58,016 --> 00:17:59,872
Then I won't be able
to get any information.

383
00:18:02,810 --> 00:18:04,700
My throat is so completely hoarse

384
00:18:04,740 --> 00:18:05,770
that I can't even roar.

385
00:18:06,370 --> 00:18:08,180
Just bring me with you.

386
00:18:08,420 --> 00:18:09,370
Erming,

387
00:18:09,770 --> 00:18:10,940
you cannot cough

388
00:18:10,980 --> 00:18:12,020
if your throat is hoarse.

389
00:18:16,810 --> 00:18:17,980
Both of you can rest assured.

390
00:18:18,290 --> 00:18:20,330
I've advanced to Soul King.

391
00:18:20,370 --> 00:18:21,328
I'm quite strong now.

392
00:18:21,420 --> 00:18:22,330
Wu,

393
00:18:22,544 --> 00:18:24,672
remember to have the skylark
to deliver a message

394
00:18:24,900 --> 00:18:26,500
if you're in danger.

395
00:18:27,260 --> 00:18:28,700
Please be extremely careful.

396
00:18:41,940 --> 00:18:43,180
This way. Come this way.

397
00:18:43,530 --> 00:18:44,220
Tang Long,

398
00:18:44,260 --> 00:18:44,770
over here.

399
00:18:47,740 --> 00:18:48,740
He's right here.

400
00:18:50,770 --> 00:18:51,180
All right.

401
00:18:51,216 --> 00:18:51,936
You can go now.

402
00:18:57,940 --> 00:18:59,370
(Tang Long, Haotian Sect Disciple)

403
00:18:59,370 --> 00:19:00,220
Where did you get

404
00:19:01,330 --> 00:19:01,850
this thing?

405
00:19:03,570 --> 00:19:04,770
You took my map.

406
00:19:04,940 --> 00:19:06,224
Shouldn't you introduce yourself

407
00:19:06,240 --> 00:19:07,680
before asking me anything?

408
00:19:07,770 --> 00:19:08,944
I don't want to hurt you.

409
00:19:09,850 --> 00:19:11,090
I'll be keeping this map.

410
00:19:11,330 --> 00:19:12,020
You can leave.

411
00:19:12,420 --> 00:19:13,740
We don't welcome outsiders here.

412
00:19:13,980 --> 00:19:15,050
I'm not an outsider.

413
00:19:15,610 --> 00:19:16,810
I only want to go home.

414
00:19:17,180 --> 00:19:18,850
Choosing the hard way, huh?

415
00:19:19,220 --> 00:19:20,660
Then don't blame me for being rude.

416
00:19:28,180 --> 00:19:28,770
Does this help

417
00:19:29,180 --> 00:19:29,980
to prove it?

418
00:19:30,220 --> 00:19:31,900
(Tang Tian, Haotian Sect Disciple)

419
00:19:32,768 --> 00:19:33,850
Which family are you from?

420
00:19:34,460 --> 00:19:35,330
Take off your mask

421
00:19:35,392 --> 00:19:36,608
and let me see you clearly.

422
00:19:37,980 --> 00:19:39,420
My Aunt is Tang Yuehua.

423
00:19:39,980 --> 00:19:41,290
She asks me to come home.

424
00:19:41,296 --> 00:19:42,480
(Tang Yu, Disciple)
You're...

425
00:19:42,496 --> 00:19:43,488
You're Tang San?

426
00:19:49,770 --> 00:19:51,770
After all this, it turns out to be you.

427
00:19:52,368 --> 00:19:54,000
Second Aunt couldn't stop praising you

428
00:19:54,080 --> 00:19:55,130
when she came back.

429
00:19:55,610 --> 00:19:57,610
She said you're even stronger than Long.

430
00:19:57,980 --> 00:19:58,900
Enough chattering.

431
00:20:00,850 --> 00:20:02,016
You can return to the sect.

432
00:20:02,500 --> 00:20:04,090
But if you're truly the son of Tang Hao,

433
00:20:04,500 --> 00:20:05,460
the sinner,

434
00:20:06,290 --> 00:20:07,660
you must be shackled.

435
00:20:25,980 --> 00:20:26,460
Follow me.

436
00:20:28,330 --> 00:20:28,850
Keep up!

437
00:20:36,420 --> 00:20:37,660
Long doesn't seem

438
00:20:37,900 --> 00:20:39,130
to like Tang San.

439
00:20:39,370 --> 00:20:40,020
Of course.

440
00:20:40,290 --> 00:20:40,980
Think about it.

441
00:20:40,992 --> 00:20:43,230
Second Aunt has been praising Long
since he was a kid.

442
00:20:43,230 --> 00:20:44,220
Now, here comes Tang San,

443
00:20:44,220 --> 00:20:45,420
who excels in everything.

444
00:20:45,420 --> 00:20:47,120
If I were him,
I wouldn't be happy either.

445
00:20:47,120 --> 00:20:48,640
Can we still catch up with them?

446
00:20:48,810 --> 00:20:50,032
We have to catch up either way.

447
00:20:50,240 --> 00:20:51,968
If we don't,
Long will surely lecture us.

448
00:20:51,980 --> 00:20:52,810
We better hurry.

449
00:21:37,050 --> 00:21:38,740
(This Haotian Sect disciple's footwork)

450
00:21:38,896 --> 00:21:40,704
(is indeed the same as Father's.)

451
00:22:15,500 --> 00:22:18,580
(Haotian Sect)

452
00:23:56,810 --> 00:23:57,420
Tang Yu!

453
00:23:57,610 --> 00:23:58,180
Tang Tian!

454
00:24:23,920 --> 00:24:25,020
Are you all right, Tang Yu?

455
00:24:25,440 --> 00:24:26,500
What about you, Tang Tian?

456
00:24:26,576 --> 00:24:27,460
I'm all right, Long.

457
00:24:27,610 --> 00:24:28,330
Where's Tang San?

458
00:24:39,370 --> 00:24:40,090
Good lad.

459
00:24:40,610 --> 00:24:41,370
I will remember

460
00:24:41,728 --> 00:24:42,848
this debt of gratitude.

461
00:24:44,500 --> 00:24:45,180
Big Brother,

462
00:24:45,810 --> 00:24:46,850
can you be gentler

463
00:24:47,050 --> 00:24:48,272
with your punch next time?

464
00:24:48,544 --> 00:24:49,460
It's pretty painful.

465
00:24:50,290 --> 00:24:52,020
You're not wrong for addressing me that.

466
00:24:52,400 --> 00:24:53,568
My name is Tang Long.

467
00:24:53,900 --> 00:24:55,330
I'm the oldest in our generation.

468
00:24:56,290 --> 00:24:57,570
They are Tang Tian and Tang Yu.

469
00:24:58,130 --> 00:24:59,940
You have saved their lives this time.

470
00:25:01,610 --> 00:25:03,104
I'm really grateful for your help.

471
00:25:03,530 --> 00:25:04,420
We're family.

472
00:25:04,480 --> 00:25:05,610
There's no need to thank me.

473
00:25:05,872 --> 00:25:07,376
Aunt said you have Twin Martial Souls.

474
00:25:07,424 --> 00:25:08,740
Was that your main martial soul,

475
00:25:08,850 --> 00:25:09,770
the Blue Silver Plant?

476
00:25:12,020 --> 00:25:13,610
Second Aunt spoke so highly of you.

477
00:25:13,940 --> 00:25:15,420
I had my doubts at first.

478
00:25:15,810 --> 00:25:16,420
Now,

479
00:25:16,480 --> 00:25:17,568
I'm really convinced.

480
00:25:18,850 --> 00:25:19,220
Let's go.

481
00:25:19,568 --> 00:25:20,928
The sect is right up there.

482
00:25:32,290 --> 00:25:32,770
Come on.

483
00:25:49,330 --> 00:25:49,740
(Father,)

484
00:25:50,810 --> 00:25:51,460
(I'm home.)

485
00:25:51,664 --> 00:25:53,088
This must be your first home.

486
00:25:53,770 --> 00:25:54,090
Hurry,

487
00:25:54,144 --> 00:25:55,440
take out our sect's token,

488
00:25:55,472 --> 00:25:56,320
and open the door.

489
00:25:56,368 --> 00:25:56,810
Token?

490
00:25:57,290 --> 00:25:57,980
What token?

491
00:25:58,500 --> 00:26:00,180
Only direct disciples of our sect

492
00:26:00,240 --> 00:26:01,760
are allowed to enter with the token.

493
00:26:02,050 --> 00:26:02,810
The outer disciples

494
00:26:02,810 --> 00:26:04,830
are all in the village
at the foot of the mountain.

495
00:26:08,900 --> 00:26:10,220
(The token of a direct disciple?)

496
00:26:11,420 --> 00:26:12,130
(Could it be...)

497
00:26:29,460 --> 00:26:29,900
Let's go.

498
00:27:00,288 --> 00:27:01,728
This is the front courtyard.

499
00:27:01,872 --> 00:27:03,570
It's only used
when the sect master calls

500
00:27:03,570 --> 00:27:04,260
for an assembly.

501
00:27:04,512 --> 00:27:05,984
The back courtyard is even bigger.

502
00:27:06,660 --> 00:27:07,980
That's where we train.

503
00:27:09,376 --> 00:27:10,850
Our sect values practical combat.

504
00:27:11,370 --> 00:27:12,848
Under the supervision of the Elders,

505
00:27:12,840 --> 00:27:14,304
the disciples undergo combat training

506
00:27:14,304 --> 00:27:15,248
to determine rankings

507
00:27:15,312 --> 00:27:16,112
based on strength.

508
00:27:16,912 --> 00:27:18,096
Since you're very skilled,

509
00:27:18,330 --> 00:27:19,570
how about a spar

510
00:27:19,616 --> 00:27:20,624
with the top disciple?

511
00:27:23,050 --> 00:27:25,050
I will spar with Big Brother
another day.

512
00:27:25,610 --> 00:27:26,530
The top disciple

513
00:27:26,740 --> 00:27:27,330
is Tang Hu.

514
00:27:28,320 --> 00:27:29,570
I've lost to him several times

515
00:27:29,770 --> 00:27:30,770
for the top rank.

516
00:27:31,520 --> 00:27:32,832
You must be careful of him.

517
00:27:33,050 --> 00:27:33,740
In the sect,

518
00:27:34,460 --> 00:27:35,330
you cannot hold back.

519
00:27:36,240 --> 00:27:37,744
Thank you for the advice, Big Brother.

520
00:27:37,900 --> 00:27:39,050
Let's go report to the Chief.

521
00:27:39,290 --> 00:27:40,980
He'll be very surprised to see you.

522
00:27:41,980 --> 00:27:42,420
Tang Tian.

523
00:27:42,740 --> 00:27:43,090
Tang Yu.

524
00:27:43,330 --> 00:27:44,500
Tell Fourth Uncle

525
00:27:44,544 --> 00:27:46,912
about the Iron Cable Bridge.
Don't delay this matter.

526
00:27:46,944 --> 00:27:48,080
- All right.
- All right.

527
00:27:49,616 --> 00:27:50,544
This way, please.

528
00:27:50,700 --> 00:27:51,130
Let's go.

529
00:27:57,296 --> 00:27:58,336
Please head inside.

530
00:27:59,040 --> 00:27:59,968
Thank you very much.

531
00:28:22,700 --> 00:28:23,420
Aunt.

532
00:28:23,850 --> 00:28:24,570
San.

533
00:28:35,140 --> 00:28:37,100
(Tang Xiao, Head of Haotian Sect)

534
00:28:43,980 --> 00:28:45,180
You're Tang San?

535
00:28:47,740 --> 00:28:48,370
I, Tang San,

536
00:28:48,740 --> 00:28:49,500
greet the Chief.

537
00:29:10,460 --> 00:29:10,900
Brother!

538
00:29:16,530 --> 00:29:19,290
Under such immense soul power pressure
from me,

539
00:29:20,700 --> 00:29:22,530
you remain completely unharmed.

540
00:29:35,770 --> 00:29:36,810
San, what are you doing?

541
00:29:40,592 --> 00:29:41,900
It's my obligation as a son

542
00:29:42,352 --> 00:29:43,460
to repay my father's debt.

543
00:29:44,700 --> 00:29:47,232
I'm willing to bear the responsibility
on my father's behalf.

544
00:29:47,776 --> 00:29:49,050
Are you capable of bearing it?

545
00:30:01,130 --> 00:30:03,500
I don't know if I can bear it.

546
00:30:04,130 --> 00:30:05,370
But I'm willing to do my best

547
00:30:06,260 --> 00:30:08,900
to shoulder the responsibilities
my father owed to the sect,

548
00:30:10,330 --> 00:30:13,090
hoping to make amends
for the harm he caused.

549
00:30:19,900 --> 00:30:20,700
Get up.

550
00:30:27,740 --> 00:30:28,850
How could you

551
00:30:29,530 --> 00:30:31,370
let a child carry your responsibilities?

552
00:30:31,680 --> 00:30:33,776
How long are you going
to keep running away,

553
00:30:33,824 --> 00:30:35,050
at fifty years old?

554
00:30:35,770 --> 00:30:36,500
Chief,

555
00:30:37,260 --> 00:30:38,260
Father isn't running.

556
00:30:38,740 --> 00:30:41,020
He just felt
he could no longer face the sect,

557
00:30:41,216 --> 00:30:43,260
which is why he sent me back
to return to our roots

558
00:30:43,376 --> 00:30:44,992
and submit to the sect's decisions.

559
00:30:46,530 --> 00:30:47,850
Return to the roots.

560
00:30:48,980 --> 00:30:50,130
That's easier said than done.

561
00:30:53,290 --> 00:30:54,370
The elders of the clan

562
00:30:54,570 --> 00:30:55,940
can't forgive your father,

563
00:30:56,130 --> 00:30:57,610
nor will they accept you.

564
00:31:00,260 --> 00:31:02,850
Your aunt and I will do our best
to make it happen.

565
00:31:03,370 --> 00:31:04,370
