572
00:31:36,260 --> 00:31:36,940
Brother,

573
00:31:37,660 --> 00:31:39,530
Second Brother forcibly removed
his soul bones

574
00:31:39,570 --> 00:31:40,330
from his body.

575
00:31:50,940 --> 00:31:53,900
(I owe the sect these two soul bones.)

576
00:31:54,330 --> 00:31:56,610
(I have failed the Haotian Sect.)

577
00:31:56,900 --> 00:31:58,256
(Please return them on my behalf.)

578
00:31:58,330 --> 00:31:59,020
Father,

579
00:31:59,220 --> 00:32:00,940
why don't you go see Uncle yourself?

580
00:32:02,020 --> 00:32:04,460
I want to spend my remaining years

581
00:32:04,570 --> 00:32:05,660
with your mother.

582
00:32:51,220 --> 00:32:53,460
Father returned the soul bones
to the sect,

583
00:32:54,090 --> 00:32:55,260
hoping that it would calm

584
00:32:55,500 --> 00:32:57,290
some anger toward him.

585
00:32:57,760 --> 00:33:00,336
It's also a closure for him
after fulfilling the responsibilities

586
00:33:00,370 --> 00:33:01,180
