into the limbs,

595
00:33:29,120 --> 00:33:31,728
temporarily freeing himself
from the torment of his old injuries.

596
00:33:32,660 --> 00:33:33,980
Now, he and my mother

597
00:33:34,260 --> 00:33:36,420
are recovering slowly
at the Ice Fire Mouth Spring.

598
00:33:37,330 --> 00:33:38,260
Uncle, don't worry.

599
00:33:38,660 --> 00:33:39,500
Your mother?

600
00:33:41,530 --> 00:33:42,570
