618
00:34:46,730 --> 00:34:47,650
It's

619
00:34:48,460 --> 00:34:50,090
because you are a part of the sect.

620
00:34:53,050 --> 00:34:53,730
Uncle.

621
00:34:56,860 --> 00:34:57,500
Yuehua,

622
00:34:58,570 --> 00:35:01,420
