634
00:35:25,500 --> 00:35:26,900
with your power.

635
00:35:28,020 --> 00:35:29,210
I have two words for you.

636
00:35:30,020 --> 00:35:30,860
Be firm.

637
00:35:43,824 --> 00:35:45,440
Aunt, you wanted to see me at this hour.

638
00:35:45,472 --> 00:35:47,360
