something to tell me?

639
00:35:48,940 --> 00:35:49,530
San,

640
00:35:51,170 --> 00:35:52,090
do you see that?

641
00:35:57,860 --> 00:35:58,730
What are those?

642
00:35:59,120 --> 00:36:01,020
The Haotian Sect disciples
who died at the hands

643
00:36:01,050 --> 00:36:02,300
of the Martial Soul Hall.

644
00:36:09,610 --> 00:36:11,940
The Haotian Sect,
once the leader of the Upper Three Sects

645
00:36:12,500 --> 00:36:13,610
is now in such a dire state

646
00:36:14,300 --> 00:36:15,780
after facing the Martial Soul Hall.

647
00:36:17,904 --> 00:36:19,530
It's even worse for the smaller sects

648
00:36:19,570 --> 00:36:20,500
on the continent now.

649
00:36:20,940 --> 00:36:21,820
At that time,

650
00:36:22,650 --> 00:36:24,688
the Martial Soul Hall pressured
the Haotian Sect,

651
00:36:26,080 --> 00:36:27,420
threatening the sect's survival.

652
00:36:27,936 --> 00:36:29,210
That's why we had no choice

653
00:36:29,250 --> 00:36:30,650
but to cut ties with your father.

654
00:36:31,380 --> 00:36:32,610
The decline of the Haotian Sect

655
00:36:33,570 --> 00:36:35,090
also began at that very moment.

656
00:36:53,500 --> 00:36:54,170
San,

657
00:36:56,704 --> 00:36:58,730
do you know
about the Four Single Attribute Tribes?

658
00:36:59,300 --> 00:37:00,250
Father told me

659
00:37:01,340 --> 00:37:04,610
they are divided into Strength,
Defense, Agility, and Destruction.

660
00:37:05,584 --> 00:37:07,952
When the Martial Soul Hall
couldn't find the Haotian Sect,

661
00:37:08,420 --> 00:37:09,940
they began to harass the four tribes.

662
00:37:10,900 --> 00:37:11,610
In the beginning,

663
00:37:11,980 --> 00:37:14,250
the disciples of the Haotian Sect
went to provide support.

664
00:37:14,736 --> 00:37:16,940
