708
00:39:02,420 --> 00:39:04,690
Everything was because
of the Martial Soul Hall's tyranny.

709
00:39:05,460 --> 00:39:07,130
They've lost Qian Xun Ji.

710
00:39:08,210 --> 00:39:09,500
You've lost your mother.

711
00:39:10,820 --> 00:39:11,860
But the other faction

712
00:39:12,250 --> 00:39:13,690
